             was indicted for <rs id="t17700711-19-off104" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17700711-19-off104" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17700711-19-off104" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
